OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter -
OL,4,Cleaving him to freeze to death
OL,6,FHe was found unresponsive in the car
OL,7,Fpark of Tesco superstore on Stratford
OL,8,FRoad shortly before 6am and he was
OL,9,Ftaken to Gloucestershire Royal
OL,10,FHospital. He died later that day.
OL,12,FGloucestershire Constabulary's Major
OL,13,FCrime Investigation Team then launched
OL,14,Fan investigation.
OL,16,FPolice say Hawkins rode away on the
OL,17,Fmobility scooter, leaving Mr Shadwick
OL,18,Fbehind in sub-zero temperatures.
