OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter -
OL,4,Cleaving him to freeze to death
OL,6,FThe scooter was later found abandoned
OL,7,Fby a member of the public on Bisley
OL,8,FOld Road in Stroud shortly before 8am
OL,9,Fthe same day.
OL,11,FAt a hearing on 25 April last year,
OL,12,FHawkins admitted to aggravated vehicle
OL,13,Ftaking without consent and assault
OL,14,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,16,FShe was remanded in custody and later
OL,17,Fcharged with manslaughter.
