OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter -
OL,4,Cleaving him to freeze to death
OL,6,FAt a hearing at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,7,FThursday 20 June, she admitted a
OL,8,Fcharge of manslaughter and was further
OL,9,Fremanded in custody.
OL,11,FA date has not yet been set for
OL,12,Fsentencing.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Adam Stacey, from
OL,15,Fthe Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Hawkins' sickening actions had
OL,17,Ftragically fatal consequences for a
OL,18,Fman whom she knew full well to be
OL,19,Fextremely vulnerable.
